'''Ootoowergs''' were [[Vegetable/Legends|vegetables]] that were often served with a [[Kommerken steak/Legends|Kommerken steak]]. When [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] visited [[Mimban/Legends|Mimban]], they ordered such a meal in a restaurant.<ref name="SOTME" />

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], a group of [[Privateer/Legends|privateers]] from the ''[[Far Orbit]]'' were to meet an [[Agent/Legends|agent]] of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] at [[Lean Nuuti Bar and Grill]] on [[StarForge Station]]. The group were to identify themselves to the [[Unidentified Ithorian (StarForge Station)|agent]] by ordering [[flangth]] and ootoowergs with [[Shasa ale]].<ref name="PW">{{WEGCite|book=The Far Orbit Project|story=Preparing for War}}</ref>

